CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 2, 1946, pg. 18 reads: "Daughter Honored - Mr. and Mrs. Richard Fields of Burrows Street honored their daughter, Nancy, with a party on her fifteenth birthday last week. The honoree and her guests are shown above. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of nine young men, and twelve young women, including fifteen-year-old Nancy Fields seated on floor behind birthday cake, posed in living room of Mr. and Mrs. Richard Fields, Burrows Street
